Distribution . Pantropical (but see below). Amphi-Atlantic: São Tomé & Príncipe ; Equatorial Guinea : Annobon Island ; Ascension Island ; throughout Caribbean Sea; Florida; Brazil : Fernando de Noronha, Atol das Rocas , Trindade & Martin Vaz Archipelago (
Christoffersen 1998 and references therein; present study
). Indo- Pacific: Madagascar to Hawaii, French Polynesia and Clipperton Island (
Banner & Banner 1982
).
